These are Puzzles for 2x7 Level 1

.:: Puzzle 2x7-Level-1-1::.
7 different brands of cigars are smoked: baccarat, havana, vegafina, prince, fonseca, ritmeester, oliveros
The people grow 7 different varities of flowers: rose, poppy, iris, azalea, aconite, daffodil, sunflower
 1. the prince-smoker is on the left of the person who growsazalea##1
 2. the person who growsaconite is the prince-smoker##1
 3. the oliveros-smoker is on the right of the ritmeester-smoker##1
 4. the person who growsiris is on the right of the person who growsdaffodil##1
 5. the vegafina-smoker is in the middle##1
 6. the person who growsrose is on the far left##1
 7. the fonseca-smoker is the person who growsrose##1
 8. the baccarat-smoker is on the right of the person who growsdaffodil##1
 9. the person who growsiris is on the left of the person who growspoppy##1
10. the person who growsazalea is on the left of the vegafina-smoker##1
11. the oliveros-smoker is on the right of the person who growspoppy##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1       |     2     |      3       |    4     |      5      |       6       |      7       |
| Cigar           | fonseca | prince | havana | vegafina | baccarat | ritmeester | oliveros |
| Flower   | rose    | aconite   | azalea      | daffodil | iris    | poppy    | sunflower         |

