.:: Puzzle 2x7-Level-1-2::.
7 different pets are kept: ferret, dog, goldfish, fish, bird, pony, lizard
7 different brands of cigars are smoked: swisher, cain, dannemann, dunhill, oliveros, prince, ritmeester
 1. the oliveros-smoker is the owner of the fish##1
 2. the owner of the pony is on the left of the ritmeester-smoker##1
 3. the prince-smoker is on the far right##1
 4. the owner of the dog is on the right of the cain-smoker##1
 5. the owner of the fish is on the right of the dunhill-smoker##1
 6. the owner of the pony is on the left of the owner of the lizard##1
 7. the oliveros-smoker is in the middle##1
 8. the oliveros-smoker is on the right of the owner of the bird##1
 9. the ritmeester-smoker is on the left of the owner of the goldfish##1
10. the owner of the fish is on the left of the swisher-smoker##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |    2     |   3   |     4     |     5     |     6      |    7     |
| Pet          | ferret | dog | bird | fish | pony | lizard | goldfish |
| Cigar   | cain      | dannemann   | dunhill   | oliveros      | swisher       | ritmeester       | prince     |

