.:: Puzzle 2x7-Level-1-3::.
The people use 7 different means of transport: motorbike, taxi, scooter, ship, boat, roller, airplane
There are 7 different favourite colors: chestnut, red, black, amber, apricot, coral, orange
 1. the person driving the taxi is on the left of the person driving the boat##1
 2. the person driving the boat is on the left of the person who likes orange##1
 3. the person who likes red is on the left of the person driving the airplane##1
 4. the person driving the motorbike is on the right of the person driving the roller##1
 5. the person who likes chestnut is the person driving the boat##1
 6. the person who likes black is on the right of the person who likes red##1
 7. the person who likes red is on the left of the person who likes black##1
 8. the person who likes red is on the right of the person who likes amber##1
 9. the person driving the roller is the person who likes amber##1
10. the person driving the scooter is on the right of the person who likes chestnut##1
11. the person who likes amber is in the middle##1
12. the person driving the airplane is on the left of the person who likes apricot##1

.:: Answer ::.
|        |    1     |     2     |   3    |      4       |     5      |    6     |     7     |
| Transport   | taxi | boat     | scooter  | roller       | motorbike       | airplane  | ship   |
| Color    | coral  | chestnut | orange | amber | red | black | apricot |

