 5. the person watching documentary movies is on the left of the person watching epic movies##1
 6. the person watching musical movies is on the far left##1
 7. the montecristo-smoker is on the right of the person watching musical movies##1
 8. the person watching western movies is on the right of the alhambra-smoker##1
 9. the person watching western movies is the oliveros-smoker##1
10. the oliveros-smoker is on the left of the person watching adventure movies##1
11. the ritmeester-smoker is the person watching adventure movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |    2     |    3     |     4      |  5   |     6      |     7     |
