.:: Puzzle 2x7-Level-1-5::.
The people's birthday is in 7 different months: january, november, june, february, october, may, december
There are 7 different nationalities: turkish, german, brazilian, spanish, australian, french, polish
 1. the person who's birthday is in november is the polish##1
 2. the german is on the right of the person who's birthday is in october##1
 3. the french is in the middle##1
 4. the australian is on the right of the brazilian##1
 5. the australian is the person who's birthday is in may##1
 6. the person who's birthday is in october is on the right of the turkish##1
 7. the french is on the left of the person who's birthday is in december##1
 8. the person who's birthday is in june is on the right of the person who's birthday is in november##1
 9. the person who's birthday is in february is on the right of the australian##1
10. the person who's birthday is in october is on the right of the person who's birthday is in december##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1    |    2    |     3      |     4     |      5      |      6       |      7      |
| Birthday   | november | june | may     | february | december | october | january |
| Nationality     | polish   | brazilian    | australian | french     | turkish         | spanish     | german        |

