.:: Puzzle 2x7-Level-1-6::.
7 different pets are kept: turtle, pony, ferret, guinea-pig, rat, snake, mouse
The people have 7 different hobbies: sudoku, baking, fishing, hiking, drawing, writing, magic-tricks
 1. the owner of the snake is on the right of the person who's hobby is hiking##1
 2. the owner of the turtle is the person who's hobby is sudoku##1
 3. the owner of the rat is on the right of the person who's hobby is baking##1
 4. the person who's hobby is sudoku is on the left of the person who's hobby is writing##1
 5. the person who's hobby is magic-tricks is on the right of the owner of the mouse##1
 6. the owner of the snake is on the left of the owner of the turtle##1
 7. the owner of the guinea-pig is in the middle##1
 8. the owner of the ferret is on the left of the person who's hobby is drawing##1
 9. the owner of the pony is on the right of the person who's hobby is magic-tricks##1
10. the owner of the ferret is on the left of the owner of the snake##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |   1    |     2      |  3  |    4     |    5    |   6   |      7      |
| Pet    | ferret | snake   | turtle | guinea-pig | mouse  | rat | pony |
| Hobby   | hiking   | drawing | sudoku | writing     | baking | magic-tricks | fishing   |

