 5. the person playing whist is on the right of the person playing snooker##1
 6. the blend-smoker is the person playing snooker##1
 7. the bluemaster-smoker is on the left of the person playing go##1
 8. the person playing monopoly is on the right of the baccarat-smoker##1
 9. the bluemaster-smoker is in the middle##1
10. the blend-smoker is on the right of the ritmeester-smoker##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1     |     2     |      3      |       4       |     5      |     6      |    7    |
| Cigar       | chaman   | baccarat | pall-mall | bluemaster | ritmeester     | blend | havana |
| Game   | poker | backgammon      | monopoly        | canasta         | go | snooker     | whist |

