There are 7 different favourite colors: apricot, coral, lavender, black, white, chestnut, green
 1. the person who likes apricot is on the right of the person drinking mirinda##1
 2. the person drinking iced-tea is on the far left##1
 3. the person drinking cola is on the right of the person who likes chestnut##1
 4. the person who likes coral is the person drinking mirinda##1
 5. the person who likes black is the person drinking iced-tea##1
 6. the person drinking lemonade is on the left of the person drinking mirinda##1
 7. the person drinking lemonade is on the right of the person drinking almond-milk##1
 8. the person drinking sprite is on the left of the person drinking cola##1
 9. the person who likes coral is in the middle##1
10. the person who likes coral is on the right of the person who likes lavender##1
11. the person who likes black is on the left of the person who likes white##1
12. the person who likes green is on the right of the person drinking sprite##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |    2     |    3    |   4    |     5     |    6    |   7    |
| Beverage          | iced-tea | almond-milk     | lemonade | mirinda | milk      | sprite  | cola |
| Color   | black   | white | lavender  | coral | apricot | chestnut | green   |

